{"tid":2311395,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍城書節逾 20 場講座、對談移師網上 12月7日一連兩周每晚七點開播","createTime":"2020-12-04T04:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T16:42:10.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"88b10b2913373d8b7426b640e5f3042380349646","tid":2311395,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:29:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%9F%8E%E6%9B%B8%E7%AF%80%E9%80%BE-20-%E5%A0%B4%E8%AC%9B%E5%BA%A7-%E5%B0%8D%E8%AB%87%E7%A7%BB%E5%B8%AB%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A-%E4%B8%80%E9%80%A3%E5%85%A9%E5%91%A8%E6%AF%8F%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%83%E9%BB%9E%E9%96%8B%E6%92%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%259F%258E%25E6%259B%25B8%25E7%25AF%2580%25E9%2580%25BE-20-%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%25BA%25A7-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25AB%2587%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%2599%259A%25E4%25B8%2583%25E9%25BB%259E%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2592%25AD%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGF%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=19bb3923\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%259F%258E%25E6%259B%25B8%25E7%25AF%2580%25E9%2580%25BE-20-%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%25BA%25A7-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25AB%2587%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%2599%259A%25E4%25B8%2583%25E9%25BB%259E%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2592%25AD%2F&h=d67e537e\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%9F%8E%E6%9B%B8%E7%AF%80%E9%80%BE-20-%E5%A0%B4%E8%AC%9B%E5%BA%A7-%E5%B0%8D%E8%AB%87%E7%A7%BB%E5%B8%AB%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A-%E4%B8%80%E9%80%A3%E5%85%A9%E5%91%A8%E6%AF%8F%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%83%E9%BB%9E%E9%96%8B%E6%92%AD/</a><br />\n<br />\n疫症之下，有人因長期待在家而看多了書，打發時間。也有人因面對這荒謬又無力的時代，更渴求知識，盼在書中找啟示，找慰藉。在還可以自由選擇看什麼書的時候，把握機會。<br />\n<br />\n去年鑑於「社會狀況不穩定」，九龍城書節宣布取消。豈料今年又遇上疫症，但這次主辦單位決定作出新嘗試，將九龍城書節移師網上舉行「Online-Booking」，聯同 20 多個書商、獨立書店製作了逾 20 場講座、對談直播、新書推介等。12月7日起一連兩周每晚七點起於Facebook 播出不同節目。九龍城書節在Facebook寫道：「在社交距離時代中，拉近與閱讀的距離」。<br />\n<br />\n九龍城書節首周有兩場直播節目，分別是「時代的文體與書寫困境」以及「禁書」。「禁書」由作家郭梓祺與「好青年荼毒室」成員鹽叔大談禁書，介紹一、兩本曾被禁的文學和哲學書，以及作者用什麼方法來避開書禁。另外錄播講座方面，有「《情感資本主義》的生成」、「謝曉虹《無遮鬼》朗讀對談」、「文學有飯開」等等，其中也有一些藝術相關的講座，如「以藝術介入歷史&mdash;&mdash;《無法憶起怎樣到達這裡》」。<br />\n<br />\n《第十二屆九龍城書節：Online-Booking》<br />\n日期：07/12 - 18/12/2020<br />\n時間：逢星期一至五 19:30 - 22:30"},{"pid":"f948db4bcdcc95b8f88dae4aa83c2b90ac177e8d","tid":2311395,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T05:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef9c4c39b60fa6444463b772f031cf2bc85bc4e","tid":2311395,"uid":12662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f948db4bcdcc95b8f88dae4aa83c2b90ac177e8d","tid":2311395,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T05:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T05:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32460851e7d19989ca17a5c2155349a793f58774","tid":2311395,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0654e291f809530d9929d9f49f224a161db875b3","tid":2311395,"uid":10570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T09:45:48.000Z","msg":"咁點買書?唔見佢有online store,定之後會有?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7baddd4b507161ad1a6d8d22af096de1a970942d","tid":2311395,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo